<p>
So I know it's not the best tomato you've seen in your life, but it's something! I gotta say that I get a motivation boost everytime I succeed in a little thing, it keeps me going and I really hope that I would continue with this.
<br/>
</p>
<img src="/assets/img/arnold.jpg"></img>
<p>
<br/>
Another thing I tried to do is to manage my time better. I wrote a project timeline for the game I want to make - Only to realise that I need to get better at digital painting. So the plan right now is to get better at digtial painting and try to do a little game in the next weekend. Also because of the COVID-19 my fulltime job workplace told everyone that if you can work from home than you should - So I guess I'll be working from home for I don't know how much time.
</p>

<p>
See you next time,
<br/>
Roy (:
